<h1>Program Overview</h1>

<p>Every quarter since its inaugural grant cycle in Fall 2008, TGIF has awarded thousands of dollars in grants to a diverse array of projects that promote sustainability and a greener tomorrow. Roughly $200,000 per year is available for student-initiated sustainability projects on campus.

